sub_title: Coach "Coaching in Change" in Excellence/Honours programme at University of Twente
summary: I am open for new career opportunities and challenges. Having rich international experiences in different positions in the higher education sector -such as programme coordinator, researcher, policy maker and manager - I would like to share my experience and skills in education- or other social service organisations. My ambition is to support policy making, management, teaching and/or consultancy and in this way to make a positive contribution to the further development and performance of the organisation I work for, including colleagues and customers. I am a dedicated and hard-working colleague with various organisational, managerial, analytical and communicative skills. Next to being a team player I also perform well independently.
